Unpacked array:unpacked array size will be change at runtime also using new() and delete keywords(vectors)
module tb;
  int arr3[3:0];
  initial
    begin
      arr3='{10,20,30,40};
      $display("size=%0d",$size(arr3));
      $display("arr3=%0p",arr3);
    end
endmodule
//output
# KERNEL: size=4
# KERNEL: arr3=10 20 30 40
